reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater to be of great quality, pretty, and comfortable, with a rich brown color. They appreciate its warmth, with one customer noting it's perfect for slightly chilly fall weather. The size receives mixed feedback, with several customers describing it as oversized. The material quality also gets mixed reviews, with some finding it soft while one customer mentions it's scratchy.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sweater
items.body: Oh my goodness!! This sweater was more than expected!! It is such nice quality, beautiful , color is true red (not candy apple ) I usually wear a large but ordered the medium, fits perfectly. I’m 5’2 with healthy hips and sweater fits loose as I wanted. Very classy look! Read more
items.author: Robbi K.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality sweater
items.body: Nice quality! It’s a little bit oversized, the way I like sweaters but if you want more form fitted, may want to size down. Read more
items.author: C Williams

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but runs big
items.body: Definitely Definitely size down! I usually wear a large, but probably could have worn a small in this sweater. It was cute, but way too big. Read more
items.author: Gina M.

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cozy Oversized Fit with a Beautiful Rich Brown Color
items.body: I’m 5’2” and 165 lbs, usually wear a medium in sweaters. I ordered my usual size and really liked the oversized fit — it’s comfy and flattering without looking too baggy. The material is a bit scratchy on the inside, so I’d probably wear a thin layer underneath. The turtleneck is also a little tighter than I’d prefer, but not a dealbreaker. Overall, I really like this sweater, especially the rich brown color — it’s warm, cozy-looking, and perfect for fall! Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish and cozy
items.body: Did not expect the sweater to be warm as it is! Perfect for slightly chilly fall weather. Runs a bit looser but that might be the style. Read more
items.author: Pankhuri Singhal

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this sweater
items.body: Love this sweater. Great quality. Soft, comfortable. I have them in several colors. Read more
items.author: Tabatha

items.title: 2.0 out of 5 stars Reeked of perfume on arrival!
items.body: This sweater arrived 12/18/25 in appropriate packaging but absolutely reeked of perfume! How can this be unless it was a previous return and repackaged and sold as " new". The sweater does look good otherwise. I am not sure I will keep it because I paid full price for what seems to be a previously worn garment . I hope someone is made aware of this and it does not happen to someone else. Read more
items.author: RoseCZena

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Green and great!

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Red, Red Brown, White, Deep Green, Beige, Black, Coffee. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
